    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>All the devices, fittings, or assemblies necessary to operate a window, such as catches, sash cords, fasteners, hinges, handles, locks, pulls, pulleys, and sash weights.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
